      "prompt_append": "Plan only — do NOT modify files or write code. BEFORE starting work, call mcp_skill('discipline'), then load your thinking skills: mcp_skill('critical-thinking'), mcp_skill('epistemic-rigor'), mcp_skill('assumption-tracker'), mcp_skill('systems-thinker'), mcp_skill('scope-management'), mcp_skill('estimation'). Then call mcp_skill(name) for EACH skill in your load_skills list. Search memory → vault → codebase before investigating. Produce a structured plan with clear task breakdown. When the plan is fully complete, output: <promise>DONE</promise>",
